node.text:
🖤🖤 Wow!!! 🖤🖤⁠
⁠
🖤On this day 5 years ago, April 16th, 2016, we opened our doors and poured our first beer. We couldn’t have made it this far without you all, and we truly feel humbled by your faithfulness and support. This past year has been difficult for everyone and we’ve had to adapt constantly, but y’all have shown up for us over and over. 🖤 We have grown and learned so much in these last 5 years and will continue to push ourselves to try new things. Let’s do another 5 my babiez! 😝🖤⁠
⁠
🖤 All Anniversary beers are online now! Head on over to www.theveilbrewing.com/anniversary. We can’t wait to see you and celebrate this special milestone. Again, thank you from the bottom of our hearts. 🙏 🖤

It has an exceptionally refined depth of barrel character and flavor that only comes with time and careful blending of different vintages. Sleeping Forever Grand Cru will only be released every 5 years and is packaged in matte black bottles, waxed dipped, black velvet labels, wrapped in a custom handkerchief, and laid to rest in special individual boxes with a faux ostrich skin exterior and red velvet interior. All you could ask for in a bourbon barrel aged Imperial Stout - layer upon layer of sweet tobacco, drippy/oily vanilla, melted dark chocolate, top-shelf bourbon, and balanced American oak. 13% ABV ⌛️☠️⚰️🐈⠀⠀
⠀⠀
⌛️☠️⚰️🐈 Available for curbside pick-up beginning today at 8 AM EST along with a bunch of other anniversary barrel aged stouts/barleywines and fresh cans(**cans are available for shipping too**). Scroll back through our posts from yesterday to see what’s dropping this week. Sleeping Forever Grand Cru will not be released for another 5 years, so make sure you grab it while you can. ⌛️☠️⚰️🐈

❤️New releases!🦌⁠
⁠⁠⁠⁠
✌️RVA on Tuesday, 8/3🙅‍♂️⁠
🍺NFK on Wednesday, 8/4⛰⁠
⁠
❌IdontwanttoBU⁴🙅‍♂️⁠
⁠
IdontwanttoBU⁴ is the quadruple dry-hopped version of our Mosaic and Citra 0 IBU IPA. Blasted with a concentrated hop character of mango and honey sweetness. 6.9% ABV.⁠
⁠
✌️Valley of Peace⛰⁠
⁠
Valley of Peace is a brand new Double IPA brewed with Citra, Strata, plus New Zealand Cascade and Nelson. Quite the lineup of amazing hops. Drippy flavors of sweet passion fruit, mango, and honey dew melon. 8% ABV.⁠
⁠
🛡War in My Mind 🗣⁠
⁠
War in My Mind is a brand new Triple India Pale Ale brewed with a generous portion of flaked wheat, malted wheat, as well as raw wheat. Hopped with Mosaic, Mosaic Cryo, Galaxy and a touch of Columbus. Impressions of sugary, ripe, exotic produce with a touch of welcomed dankness. 11% ABV.⁠
⁠
❤️Never Never Again Again❤️⁠
⁠
Never Never Again Again is a Gose Ale with double raspberry purée. A raspberry purée bomb reminiscent of summer time push pops. 5.1% ABV.⁠
⁠
🦌 Schröderhaüst 🍺 ⁠
⁠
Schröderhaüst is a brand new Bavarian-inspired Wheat Ale aka Weissebier. Step mashed, and gently hopped with select German Noble hops, this beer is inspired by one of our favorite German brewers of this style. Extremely refreshing with lovely esters of banana and spice with the perfect touch of  effervescence, dryness, and subtle bitterness. 5.1% ABV.⁠
⁠
⁠
NO LIMITS. See you Tuesday for these!

🐇We’re super stoked for the release of our collaboration with @dogfishhead! 🐇⁠
⁠
Realizationz and Dreamz🧠💤🐇⁠
⁠
Realizationz and Dreamz is a beer brewed in collaboration with our friends at @dogfishhead back in February of 2018. Some of you may remember a peppercorn Double IPA that we released back then called Dreamz and Realizationz. Well we brewed another batch of the exact same beer but this time we did a turbid mash and instead of fermenting it in a stainless tank with our usual ale yeast we sent it to our rooftop koelschip for overnight natural cooling and inoculation. The next day we filled freshly emptied French oak red wine barrels of the beer and allowed it to spontaneously ferment and age quietly at our wild facility for 29 months! The intense hoppiness of the beer allowed it to withstand the affects of the wild yeast and bacteria for some time, but eventually it developed a great acidity and complex flavor profile that we are super excited about. Before bottling we extracted the barrels onto fresh Nelson Sauvin and Enigma dry hops for an extra punch of hoppiness. Realizationz and Dreamz is exactly what we set out to create together with @dogfishhead - a beer that reminds us equally of a great India Pale Ale and a Lambic-inspired spontaneously fermented beer. It bursts from the glass with notes of bright flowers, peppercorn, and honey suckle sweetness. Bottle-conditioned with no additional yeast for 12 months. 9% ABV. $15.00+tax each. 750ml bottles. ⁠
⁠
Available for shipping and RVA starting tomorrow and NFK Wednesday. 🧠💤🐇⁠
⁠
See y’all tomorrow!

Imaginary Hug🫂💭⁠

Imaginary Hug is a brand new IPA singularly hopped with Mosaic. Bursting with notes of fruit loops, stone fruit skin, with a pleasant grapefruit finish. 6% ABV. $14.50+tax/4pack. ⁠
⁠
Heal Me🩹🩺⁠
⁠
Heal Me is a DIPA brewed with Citra, Galaxy, Motueka, and BRU-1. Notes of overripe, pithy citrus, strawberry, soft and juicy orange juice pulp. 8.5% ABV. $17.50+tax/4pack. ⁠
⁠
This World Is Not Real🗺🌍⁠
⁠
This World Is Not Real is our DIPA with Citra, Mosaic, Nelson, and Enigma. A well-blended flavor combo of musky cantaloupe, kiwi, and exotic papaya.  8% ABV. $17.50+tax/4pack. ⁠
⁠
Purple Paradise Punch Tastee🥭🍍🥊🌴⁠
⁠
Purple Paradise Punch Tastee is a brand new Smoothie-style Sour Ale brewed with mango, apricot, pineapple, and butterfly pea powder. Tastes like apricot and peach cobbler with a deceivingly purple color and nice tartness. 5.5% ABV. $22.00+tax/4pack. ⁠
⁠
Ever Gonnageti🫐🥤🥣⁠
⁠
Ever Gonnagetit is a brand new Non-Alcoholic Gose! Brewed in the style of your favorite Veil Gose, but with less booze! Crushed with raspberry, blackberry, and boysenberry purées. Intense impressions of freshly picked mixed berries and açaí bowls. 0.4% ABV. $12.00+tax/4pack. ⁠
⁠
